[{"id": 521958, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4546, "text": "DE SOM f\u00f6rnekar sanningen och som hindrar [andra] att f\u00f6lja Guds v\u00e4g - allt vad [s\u00e5dana m\u00e4nniskor] har \u00e5stadkommit skall Han l\u00e5ta g\u00e5 f\u00f6rlorat."}, {"id": 521960, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4547, "text": "Men de troende som lever ett r\u00e4ttskaffens liv och tror p\u00e5 det som har uppenbarats f\u00f6r Muhammad - detta \u00e4r sanningen fr\u00e5n deras Herre - deras d\u00e5liga handlingar skall Han utpl\u00e5na och Han skall ge dem sinnesstyrka och inre lugn."}, {"id": 521961, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4548, "text": "S\u00e5 [\u00e4r det] d\u00e4rf\u00f6r att de som vill f\u00f6rneka sanningen f\u00f6ljer det som \u00e4r falskt och bedr\u00e4gligt, men de som tror f\u00f6ljer den sanning [som de f\u00e5tt] fr\u00e5n sin Herre. Gud visar ocks\u00e5 med exempel hur m\u00e4nniskorna g\u00e5r till v\u00e4ga."}, {"id": 521962, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4549, "text": "D\u00c5 NI m\u00f6ter f\u00f6rnekarna [i strid], l\u00e5t [sv\u00e4rden] falla \u00f6ver deras huvuden till dess ni har tvingat dem p\u00e5 kn\u00e4; tag d\u00e4refter [de \u00f6verlevande] till f\u00e5nga. Sedan [kommer den tid] d\u00e5 ni skall ge dem fria, godvilligt eller mot l\u00f6sen, f\u00f6r att kriget skall l\u00e4gga av sina b\u00f6rdor. Detta [\u00e4r vad ni har att iaktta]. Om Gud ville kunde Han helt visst sl\u00e5 ned dem [utan er medverkan], men genom att l\u00e5ta er k\u00e4mpa mot varandra s\u00e4tter Han er alla p\u00e5 prov. Och vad dem betr\u00e4ffar som stupar i kampen f\u00f6r Guds sak, skall Han inte l\u00e5ta deras handlingar bli f\u00f6rg\u00e4ves;"}, {"id": 521963, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4550, "text": "Han skall leda deras [steg] och ge dem sinnesstyrka och inre lugn"}, {"id": 521964, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4551, "text": "och f\u00f6ra dem till paradiset som Han har l\u00e5tit dem veta."}, {"id": 521965, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4552, "text": "Troende! Om ni ger Gud er hj\u00e4lp skall Han \u00f6ka [er styrka] och g\u00f6ra er stadiga p\u00e5 foten."}, {"id": 521966, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4553, "text": "Men el\u00e4nde v\u00e4ntar dem som framh\u00e4rdar i att f\u00f6rneka sanningen och allt vad de har \u00e5stadkommit skall Han l\u00e5ta g\u00e5 f\u00f6rlorat"}, {"id": 521967, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4554, "text": "- d\u00e4rf\u00f6r att de k\u00e4nner motvilja mot det som Gud har uppenbarat - och s\u00e5 [l\u00e5ter Han] alla deras f\u00f6retag g\u00e5 om intet."}, {"id": 521968, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4555, "text": "Har de aldrig begett sig ut i v\u00e4rlden och sett [sp\u00e5ren som visar] hur slutet blev f\u00f6r deras f\u00f6reg\u00e5ngare? Gud l\u00e4t dem g\u00e5 under och detsamma skall h\u00e4nda alla som f\u00f6rnekar sanningen;"}, {"id": 521969, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 507, "ruku": 442, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4556, "text": "detta d\u00e4rf\u00f6r att Gud \u00e4r de troendes Beskyddare, men f\u00f6rnekarna har ingen beskyddare."}, {"id": 521970, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 508, "ruku": 443, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4557, "text": "De troende som lever ett r\u00e4ttskaffens liv skall Gud f\u00f6ra till lustg\u00e5rdar, vattnade av b\u00e4ckar, men de som framh\u00e4rdar i att f\u00f6rneka sanningen skall [under en tid] f\u00e5 njuta av livet och inta sin f\u00f6da som boskapen betar; d\u00e4refter skall [den eviga] Elden bli deras slutliga boning."}, {"id": 521971, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 508, "ruku": 443, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4558, "text": "Hur m\u00e5nga folk med st\u00f6rre makt \u00e4n ditt [Muhammad] som har jagat bort dig, har Vi inte l\u00e5tit g\u00e5 under! Och de fick ingen hj\u00e4lp!"}, {"id": 521972, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 508, "ruku": 443, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4559, "text": "KAN DEN som st\u00f6der sig p\u00e5 ett klart vittnesb\u00f6rd fr\u00e5n sin Herre j\u00e4mf\u00f6ras med den vars d\u00e5liga handlingar sk\u00f6nm\u00e5lats f\u00f6r honom och som [bara] f\u00f6ljer vad de sj\u00e4lva tycker och \u00f6nskar"}, {"id": 521973, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 508, "ruku": 443, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4560, "text": "Paradiset som lovats dem som fruktar Gud kan liknas vid [en lustg\u00e5rd] d\u00e4r b\u00e4ckar flyter med vatten som alltid f\u00f6rblir friskt, och floder av mj\u00f6lk med of\u00f6rd\u00e4rvad smak, och floder av det ljuvligaste vin, och floder av renaste honung, och d\u00e4r de skall njuta frukter av alla slag och [dessutom f\u00e5] sin Herres f\u00f6rl\u00e5telse. [Kan den som stiger in i detta paradis j\u00e4mf\u00f6ras] med den som m\u00e5ste f\u00f6rbli i Elden och [d\u00e4r] dricka sk\u00e5llhett vatten, som br\u00e4nner s\u00f6nder hans in\u00e4lvor"}, {"id": 521974, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 508, "ruku": 443, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4561, "text": "Bland [hycklarna] finns de som lyssnar till dig [Muhammad, och l\u00e5tsas f\u00f6rst\u00e5], men n\u00e4r de g\u00e5r ifr\u00e5n dig s\u00e4ger de till dem som har kunskap: \"Vad betyder det han sade nyss?\" De \u00e4r [m\u00e4nniskor] vars hj\u00e4rtan Gud har f\u00f6rseglat, eftersom de [bara] f\u00f6ljer vad de sj\u00e4lva tycker och \u00f6nskar;"}, {"id": 521975, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 508, "ruku": 443, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4562, "text": "men de som vill l\u00e5ta sig v\u00e4gledas, dem ger Han en allt fastare ledning och f\u00f6rdjupar deras gudsfruktan."}, {"id": 521976, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 508, "ruku": 443, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4563, "text": "V\u00e4ntar de bara att den Yttersta stunden skall komma \u00f6ver dem pl\u00f6tsligt? Men dess f\u00f6rebud \u00e4r redan h\u00e4r! Och vad har de f\u00f6r nytta av att dra sig till minnes, n\u00e4r Stunden \u00e4r \u00f6ver dem?"}, {"id": 521977, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 508, "ruku": 443, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4564, "text": "H\u00e5ll fast vid din kunskap att det inte finns n\u00e5gon gud utom Gud; be Honom om f\u00f6rl\u00e5telse f\u00f6r dina synder och [be om f\u00f6rl\u00e5telse] f\u00f6r alla troende m\u00e4n och kvinnor! Gud vet vad ni dagligen bekymrar er om och m\u00e5let d\u00e4r ni [till sist] f\u00e5r vila."}, {"id": 521978, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4565, "text": "DE TROENDE s\u00e4ger: \"Varf\u00f6r har inget budskap [med befallning att g\u00e5 till strid] \u00e4nnu uppenbarats?\" Men n\u00e4r ett budskap med fasta och klara f\u00f6reskrifter om krig uppenbaras, ser du [Muhammad] hur de som har tvivlets sjuka i sina hj\u00e4rtan ser p\u00e5 dig med den slocknade blicken hos den som \u00e4r n\u00e4ra d\u00f6den. Men vad de b\u00f6r g\u00f6ra \u00e4r att"}, {"id": 521979, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4566, "text": "lyda [dig] och s\u00e4ga de r\u00e4tta orden; n\u00e4r [Gud] har f\u00e4llt avg\u00f6randet \u00e4r det b\u00e4st f\u00f6r dem att [k\u00e4mpa och] lita p\u00e5 Hans ord."}, {"id": 521980, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4567, "text": "Skall man kanske v\u00e4nta av er - om ni v\u00e4nder ryggen [\u00e5t Profeten och hans budskap] - att ni [g\u00e5r tillbaka till ert gamla liv och] st\u00f6r ordningen p\u00e5 jorden och sprider sedef\u00f6rd\u00e4rv och river itu alla familjeband?"}, {"id": 521981, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4568, "text": "Det \u00e4r [m\u00e4nniskor som] dessa som Gud utest\u00e4nger fr\u00e5n Sin n\u00e5d och som Han ber\u00f6var h\u00f6rsel och syn."}, {"id": 521982, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4569, "text": "T\u00e4nker de alls inte p\u00e5 vad Koranen [har att s\u00e4ga]? Eller har de dragit f\u00f6r regeln f\u00f6r sina hj\u00e4rtan"}, {"id": 521983, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4570, "text": "DE SOM v\u00e4nde om efter att ha [antagit tron och] f\u00e5tt den raka v\u00e4gen klart utpekad f\u00f6r sig, f\u00f6rleddes till detta av Dj\u00e4vulen som ingav dem bedr\u00e4gliga f\u00f6rhoppningar;"}, {"id": 521984, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4571, "text": "och detta [till f\u00f6ljd av] att de har sagt till dem som s\u00e5g med avsky p\u00e5 vad Gud uppenbarade [f\u00f6r Muhammad]: \"Vi skall f\u00f6lja er i en del av detta.\" Men Gud k\u00e4nner deras hemligheter."}, {"id": 521985, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4572, "text": "Hur [skall de f\u00f6rh\u00e5lla sig] n\u00e4r d\u00f6ds\u00e4nglarna h\u00e4mtar deras sj\u00e4lar medan de sl\u00e5r dem i ansiktet och i ryggen?"}, {"id": 521986, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 444, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4573, "text": "Detta [m\u00e5ste de utst\u00e5] d\u00e4rf\u00f6r att allt det som de str\u00e4var efter \u00e4r s\u00e5dant som v\u00e4cker Guds vrede, och d\u00e4rf\u00f6r att de avskyr allt det som Gud ser med v\u00e4lbehag; och s\u00e5 [l\u00e5ter Han] alla deras f\u00f6retag g\u00e5 \u00f6verstyr."}, {"id": 521987, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 509, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4574, "text": "Eller tror de vars hj\u00e4rtan \u00e4r angripna av tvivlets sjuka att Gud inte skall l\u00e5ta deras avund och illvilja [mot de troende] dras fram i ljuset?"}, {"id": 521988, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4575, "text": "Om Vi hade velat kunde Vi ha visat dig dem s\u00e5 att du med [ledning av] deras k\u00e4nnetecken visste vilka de var; men p\u00e5 deras tal kommer du med s\u00e4kerhet att k\u00e4nna igen dem. Gud k\u00e4nner era handlingar."}, {"id": 521989, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4576, "text": "Helt visst skall Vi s\u00e4tta er p\u00e5 prov s\u00e5 att de bland er som vill str\u00e4va och k\u00e4mpa [f\u00f6r Guds sak] och de t\u00e5lmodiga och uth\u00e5lliga f\u00e5r ge sig till k\u00e4nna, och Vi skall pr\u00f6va [hur uppriktiga ni \u00e4r i] era f\u00f6rklaringar."}, {"id": 521990, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 203, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4577, "text": "De som framh\u00e4rdar i att f\u00f6rneka sanningen och hindra [andra] att f\u00f6lja Guds v\u00e4g och som trotsar och v\u00e4nder ryggen \u00e5t [Hans] S\u00e4ndebud, sedan de f\u00e5tt den raka v\u00e4gen klart utpekad f\u00f6r sig, kommer inte att v\u00e5lla Gud skada och Han skall l\u00e5ta alla deras f\u00f6retag g\u00e5 om intet."}, {"id": 521991, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 204, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4578, "text": "Troende! Lyd Gud och lyd S\u00e4ndebudet och l\u00e5t inte era [goda] handlingar g\u00e5 f\u00f6rlorade!"}, {"id": 521992, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 204, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4579, "text": "De som framh\u00e4rdar i att f\u00f6rneka sanningen och hindra [andra] att f\u00f6lja Guds v\u00e4g och som d\u00f6r som f\u00f6rnekare, skall inte f\u00e5 f\u00f6rl\u00e5telse av Gud."}, {"id": 521993, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 204, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4580, "text": "OCH TAPPA inte modet [n\u00e4r ni k\u00e4mpar f\u00f6r Guds sak] och tigg inte om fred; [p\u00e5 grund av er tro] har ni \u00f6vertaget och Gud \u00e4r med er och Han skall inte l\u00e5ta er g\u00e5 miste om [n\u00e5got av det som ni har f\u00f6rtj\u00e4nat med] era handlingar."}, {"id": 521994, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 204, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4581, "text": "Detta jordiska liv \u00e4r [inte mycket mer \u00e4n] lek och flyktig gl\u00e4dje, men om ni tror [p\u00e5 Gud] och fruktar Honom, skall Han ge er full l\u00f6n. Han beg\u00e4r inte att ni [offrar f\u00f6r Hans sak allt] vad ni \u00e4ger."}, {"id": 521995, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 204, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4582, "text": "Beg\u00e4rde Han detta av er och f\u00f6rvandlade er till barfota [tiggare], skulle er sn\u00e5lhet ta \u00f6verhanden och s\u00e5 skulle Han driva fram det s\u00e4msta inom er."}, {"id": 521996, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 47, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Muhammad", "surah_en_name_translation": "Muhammad", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 510, "ruku": 445, "hizb_quarter": 204, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4583, "text": "[Troende!] N\u00e4r ni [nu] uppmanas att ge av vad ni \u00e4ger f\u00f6r Guds sak, ger n\u00e5gra av er prov p\u00e5 sn\u00e5lhet; men med sin sn\u00e5lhet skadar den sn\u00e5le bara sig sj\u00e4lv; [gl\u00f6m inte att] Gud \u00e4r den Rike [som inte beh\u00f6ver era g\u00e5vor], men ni \u00e4r de fattiga [som beh\u00f6ver Honom i allt]. Om ni v\u00e4nder er [ifr\u00e5n Honom], skall Han l\u00e5ta andra m\u00e4nniskor inta er plats, och de kommer inte att likna er."}]